2011年11月25日，意大利外长Giulio Terzi di Sant'Agata表示意大利支持SNC等叙反对派组织<ref name="italysnc">{{cite web|url=http://www.ansa.it/ansamed/en/news/sections/ministry/2011/11/25/visualizza_new.html_14006144.html |title=Syria: Terzi, Italy support for organised opposition |date=2011-11-25 |publisher=ansamed.info}}</ref><ref name="ItalyWantsSanctions">{{cite web|url=http://www.kuna.net.kw/NewsAgenciesPublicSite/ArticleDetails.aspx?id=2207928&Language=en|title=Italy seeks tougher sanctions against Syrian regime -- FM|date=2011-11-25|publisher=[[Kuwait_News_Agency|Kuwait News Agency]]|accessdate=2012-01-27|archive-date=2013-01-11|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130111203804/http://www.kuna.net.kw/NewsAgenciesPublicSite/ArticleDetails.aspx?id=2207928&Language=en|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。12月11日，他与Burhan Ghalioun会面时说意大利将加强与SNC的联系，因为SNC是一个重要的反对派组织。

2011年12月2日，[[保加利亚|保加利亚]]外长宣布SNC“是关于叙利亚未来的一个重要的对话伙伴”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sofiaecho.com/2011/12/03/1218158_un-human-rights-council-strongly-condemns-abuses-by-syrian-authorities|title=UN Human Rights Council strongly condemns abuses by Syrian authorities|date=2011-12-03|accessdate=2011-11-28|publisher=Sofia Echo|archive-date=2013-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728225735/http://www.sofiaecho.com/2011/12/03/1218158_un-human-rights-council-strongly-condemns-abuses-by-syrian-authorities|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2011年12月5日，[[美国国务卿|美国国务卿]][[希拉里·罗德姆·克林顿|希拉里·克林頓]]表示：叙全国委员会是一个“寻求和平民主转变的主要且合法的叙利亚代表”，美国“承诺要帮助……实现这个转变”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/12/06/world/meast/clinton-syrian-opposition/index.html|title=Clinton to Syrian opposition: Ousting al-Assad is only first step in transition|date=2011-12-06|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2011-12-21|archive-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517092842/https://www.cnn.com/2011/12/06/world/meast/clinton-syrian-opposition/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/clinton-meets-with-syria-opposition/2011/12/06/gIQApzQ9ZO_story.html|title=Clinton meets with Syria opposition|date=2011-12-06|publisher=Washington Post|accessdate=2011-12-21|archive-date=2019-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190516052801/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/clinton-meets-with-syria-opposition/2011/12/06/gIQApzQ9ZO_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年12月9日到11日，SNC代表团访问[[挪威|挪威]][[奥斯陆|奥斯陆]]，与挪威政府官员与人道主义组织会面。挪威外长积极回应SNC代表团的要求<ref>{{cite web |url=http://syriancouncil.org/en/news/item/446-snc-delegation-meets-norwegian-foreign-ministry.html |title=SNC Delegation Meets Norwegian Foreign Ministry |date=2011-12-08 |accessdate=2012-01-21 |publisher=Syrian National Council |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223001825/http://www.syriancouncil.org/en/news/item/446-snc-delegation-meets-norwegian-foreign-ministry.html |archivedate=2012-02-23 }}</ref>。

2011年12月14日，敘全国委员会在[[土耳其|土耳其]][[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]正式建立起自己的第一个外交办事处<ref name="Istanbul office">{{cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2011/12/201112149810909861.html |title=Syria's opposition opens office in Turkey |date=2011-12-14 |accessdate=2011-12-21 |publisher=Al Jazeera |archive-date=2011-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111222040552/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2011/12/201112149810909861.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年12月16日，[[加拿大|加拿大]]外长John Baird在[[加拿大众议院|众议院]]上表示“巴沙尔·阿萨德政府将倒台，这只是时间问题”。23日，他与Burhan Ghalioun率领的SNC代表团会面，SNC也很感谢加拿大政府对于他们的支持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://syriancouncil.org/en/news/item/1-snc-delegation-meets-candas-minister-of-foreign-affairs.html|title=SNC Delegation Meets Canada's Minister of Foreign Affairs|date=2011-12-23|accessdate=2012-01-21|publisher=Syrian National Council|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120108181814/http://syriancouncil.org/en/news/item/1-snc-delegation-meets-candas-minister-of-foreign-affairs.html|archivedate=2012-01-08}}</ref>。

